The paper deals with distributed algorithms for coverage problems, which are central in optimization and have applications in data mining and machine learning. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Information Theory (cs.IT).
